data.description: Beautiful 3 bed 2.5 bath in a gated community of Skye Canyon.  The neighborhood is fantastic with a community club, workout facility, pool, parks, and much more.  The home has a wonderful layout with large rooms and an open floor plan.  It comes with appliances and it has a tankless water heater!  There are tons of upgrades and a kitchen to die for.  Come and see!
